    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone seeking a reliable daily driver who isn't overly concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the paint has begun to fade on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear and minor staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, making it a solid, functional choice for commuting or running errands.",
