    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standard. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as intended, making this an exceptional find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in absolute peak condition.",
