      "description": "We are pleased to offer this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic discipline. This automobile has been curated to meet the standards of the discerning driver, featuring a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior that reflects consistent, professional care. While it displays the subtle character of a seasoned road-goer, its performance remains sharp and its presentation authoritative. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a dependable, high-caliber asset that balances sophisticated engineering with practical value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
